text: Eltun Turabov (; born on 18 February 1997 in Baku) is an Azerbaijani football midfielder who plays for Sumgayit in the Azerbaijan Premier League. ==Career== ===Club=== On 26 July 2019, Sabah was announced that Turabov had joined Albanian club Bylis on a season-long loan deal. He made his professional debut for Bylis in the Albanian Superliga on 24 August 2019, starting in the away match against Teuta.
